Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • abstract_classes.Entity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bubble, Drawer, Image, Message, MovingEntity, Rect

    public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents an Entity in the game. Something that will appear on the screen.
    Author:
    Alexander J Mills
